      "link": null,
      "locked": false,
      "text": "- charged when a message is delivered\n(not sent).\n\n- charged based on who the message is\nsent to and the category of the\nmessage.\n\nThere are four message categories on\nthe WhatsApp Business Platform: \n\n- marketing \n-utility \n-authentication \n-service\n\nrates vary by market – category pair",
      "fontSize": 20,
      "fontFamily": 5,
      "textAlign": "left",
      "verticalAlign": "top",
      "containerId": null,
      "originalText": "- charged when a message is delivered (not sent).\n\n- charged based on who the message is sent to and the category of the message.\n\nThere are four message categories on the WhatsApp Business Platform: \n\n- marketing \n-utility \n-authentication \n-service\n\nrates vary by market – category pair",
      "autoResize": false,
      "lineHeight": 1.25
    },
